{
  "texts": [
    "We further connected the DSC scores corresponding to the same task of the four models with the podium plot Fig. 3b, which is complementary to the box plot.",
    "In the upper part, each colored dot denotes the median DSC achieved with the respective method on one task.",
    "Dots corresponding to identical test cases are connected by a line.",
    "In the lower part, the frequency of achieved ranks for each method is presented with bar charts.",
    "It can be found that MedSAM ranked in first place on most tasks, surpassing the performance of the U-Net and DeepLabV3+ specialist models that have a high frequency of ranks with second and third places, respectively, In contrast, SAM ranked last place in almost all tasks."
  ]
}